[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]是[[任天堂|任天堂]]出品的[[电子游戏机|电子游戏机]]，支持实体和数字版游戏。实体版游戏载体为[[ROM卡带|卡带]]<ref name="polygon-gamecards2">{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/10/20/13344618/nintendo-switch-nx-games-cartridges|title=Nintendo Switch will use cartridges|website=Polygon|publisher=Vox Media|accessdate=2016-10-20|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020142412/http://www.polygon.com/2016/10/20/13344618/nintendo-switch-nx-games-cartridges|dead-url=no}}</ref>，数字版游戏由[[任天堂eShop|任天堂eShop]]销售，储存在32 GB内建储存器或[[SD卡|microSD]]卡中<ref name="shacknews specs">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/98546/nintendo-switch-has-a-720p-screen-32-gb-of-storage-and-expandable-storage-via-microsdxc-cards | title = Nintendo Switch has a 720p screen, 32 GB of storage, and expandable storage via microSDXC cards | first = David | last = Craddock | date = 2017-01-13 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | work = Shacknews | archive-date = 2017-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170114201327/http://www.shacknews.com/article/98546/nintendo-switch-has-a-720p-screen-32-gb-of-storage-and-expandable-storage-via-microsdxc-cards | dead-url = no }}</ref>。除中國大陸外，任天堂Switch不再[[锁区|锁区]]，可游玩任意区域的游戏<ref name="polygon specs">{{cite web | url = http://www.polygon.com/2017/1/13/14241898/nintendo-switch-details | title = Everything we know about Nintendo Switch | first = Allegra | last = Frank | date = 2017-01-13 | accessdate = 2017-01-13 | work = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | archive-date = 2017-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170114042835/http://www.polygon.com/2017/1/13/14241898/nintendo-switch-details | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

